{"tid":913244,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《鐵馬尋橋》兄弟團祝嘉穎當爸 唐詩詠：一定錫到BB燶","createTime":"2018-11-23T08:59:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-24T05:20:57.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"46219b9a7b396b807b1ee93fced9572ad189827a","tid":913244,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:59:04.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】對於鄭嘉穎及陳凱琳宣佈有喜，《鐵馬尋橋》兄弟團均送上祝福，唐詩詠說：「恭喜嘉穎，今年他最想有的兩樣事物（指老婆及BB）都有了，這個BB一定是萬千寵愛在一身，我們一班兄弟姊妹一定錫到BB燶！」馬國明則說：「恭喜恭喜！祝BB身體健康，一家人平平安安、幸福快樂。」更附上3個錫錫表情，想必也如詩詠所說「錫到燶」！<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/WbQxqm.qShBL29DdyPNVhA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20181123f144706.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FWbQxqm.qShBL29DdyPNVhA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20181123f144706.jpg&h=5eeed2d8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"892021bb60c904b1db49b2ef70a19a336f4c6649","tid":913244,"uid":38904,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T09:00:57.000Z","msg":"隻臭雞要借陳凱琳上報<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"994629aa95f3c6b7b7b0201c7b134752c5088d82","tid":913244,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T09:06:16.000Z","msg":"個b老豆同公公差唔多一樣大<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03dd385fdbf3da4a1a045ab2872c96fc1c18636b","tid":913244,"uid":277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T00:02:21.000Z","msg":"顧汝章<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6401dec1a4b4b75015f760bab8184645b7602fa","tid":913244,"uid":48251,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018